oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Frost Bros. Job No. 33710
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:subject: Accounting; Hatch Show Print (Firm);
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Invoice (No. 2258) for an order placed for the Frost Brothers by Don Frost for 50 one color window cards for a Big Gospel Concert at the Courthouse in Henderson, Tennessee, on January 1. Receipt indicates the agreed price, quantity, shipping method, and a description of the posters.
